      "rationale": "The SST k-ω turbulence model and power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) were selected based on published literature for centrifugal pump hemolysis prediction. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2; the selection rationale is documented in the modeling report."
